articles.author: Emilee Speck
articles.title: Axiom Space prepares for first launch with all-European crew - Fox Weather
articles.description: Axiom Space plans to launch its third private astronaut mission to the International Space Station as soon as Wednesday from Florida, marking the first time an all-European commercial crew is headed to the orbiting laboratory.
